 * CrowdStrike Service
 *
 * Handles API calls for CrowdStrike Falcon vulnerability lookup functionality
 *
 * Related to: Feature 015-we-have-currently (CrowdStrike System Vulnerability Lookup)
 * Tasks: T029-T030 [US1-Impl], T052-T054 [US3-Impl]
